While Tiffany is the umbrella brand, we have several sub brands catering to different target groups with major power brands being Chunko’s, Nutty Bites, Delights range, Cookie Monsta, Oatsville, Marie & Digestive. Our current positioning in the market is affordable, top quality biscuits, with something for everyone in the family. Tiffany has been recently recognized as the most preferred food brand in the UAE in the 2020 release of the Kantar Brand Footprint study. Product description: Indomie Mi Goreng is an instant noodles product line made under the Indomie brand by the Indofood company, the world's largest instant noodle manufacturer, located in Indonesia. Mi Goreng is Indonesian for "fried noodle". Indomie Mi Goreng is simply abbreviated as Indomie goreng by most Indonesians. Indomie Goreng is a type of instant noodle served without soup and is stirred well with soysauce, oil, and seasoning. This instant noodle derived its inspiration from traditional Indonesian dish called mi goreng, a variant of fried noodle common in Indonesia. Cooking Instructions: • Empty Mie noodles into 300-400 ml of brisky boiling water & simmer for 3 minutes. • Add flavoring: Seasoning powder, seasoning oil, chili powder and stir gently until dissolved. • Indomie is Ready to be served.
